.SH NAME
LAPACK-3 - CLA_GBRCOND_C Compute the infinity norm condition number of  op(A) * inv(diag(C)) where C is a REAL vector
.SH SYNOPSIS
.TP 14
REAL FUNCTION
CLA_GBRCOND_C( TRANS, N, KL, KU, AB, LDAB, AFB,
LDAFB, IPIV, C, CAPPLY, INFO, WORK,
RWORK )
